ðŸŽ¨ style.css

/* ========== Global Styles ========== */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
  background: #f9f9f9;
}

/* ========== Header (Flexbox) ========== */
.header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between; /* logo left, nav right */
  align-items: center;
  background: #222;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
}

.header .logo {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.nav ul {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  list-style: none;
}

.nav a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.nav a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

/* ========== Hero Section ========== */
.hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 3rem 1rem;
  background: #4cafef;
  color: #fff;
}

.hero .btn {
  margin-top: 1rem;
  padding: 0.7rem 1.2rem;
  border: none;
  background: #222;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

.hero .btn:hover {
  background: #444;
}

/* ========== Grid Layout (Main Content) ========== */
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); /* 4 equal columns */
  gap: 1rem;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.card {
  background: #fff;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* ========== Footer (Flexbox) ========== */
.footer {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between; /* text left, social right */
  align-items: center;
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
  background: #222;
  color: #fff;
}

/* ========== Responsive Breakpoints ========== */

/* Tablet: 768px */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .grid-container {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 2 columns */
  }

  .nav ul {
    gap: 1rem;
  }
}

/* Mobile: 480px */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .header {
    flex-direction: column; /* stack logo & nav */
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .nav ul {
    flex-direction: column; /* vertical nav */
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .grid-container {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* single column */
  }

  .footer {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
 shown:

Flexbox â†’ header, nav, footer

Grid â†’ card layout in main content

Media Queries â†’ responsive behavior for tablet (2 columns) and mobile (1 column + stacked flex items)

Clean CSS with comments for maintainability


               

